review 1: The first time I come to this place. I ordered Rujak Kuah Pindang GULA, but when it was coming they gave me "rujak kuah pindang" with no sweet taste, it was just salty. Luckily, the ambience was nice (downstair seats). I don't really recommend this place to eat rujak. Maybe that day wasn't my good day. The rest was just so so.

address: 9696+53F, Jl. Ahmad Yani Utara, Dauh Puri Kaja, Kec. Denpasar Utara, Kota Denpasar, Bali 80233, Indonesia
review 1:
I love the interior design. Such as a cozy place and good place to dine in. The bread so various and taste good. Fresh from the oven. But dunno about the halal. They didn't put the Halal sign (Or... Did I miss something?). But I know Conato isn't only in Bali so... I assume it's Halal? Or better put the halal sign so you can attract more visitors.
But a little advice, set the Air Conditioner cooler so I'll stay longer üòãüòãüòã
After all.
I love eat in this place alone!
Recommended
review 2: The design of the building resembles a cafe as if to emphasize that this place not only sells bread ... but also can be a choice of places to enjoy coffee and other snacks. a large enough parking lot (fit around 2-3 cars of 5 passengers) on the edge of the A. yani road which is indeed crowded. In essence, this place is good enough for bread shopping or hang out and eat right on the spot, because the place is quite comfortable as well.
review 3:
Nice place to go for a bakery.

The place feels warm and d best part, it is clean. The bread counters are also cleaned every few hours. Staff are also friendly and attentive.

And if u are slightly hungrier, there is an option to buy the burgers and sandwiches too. We did buy them and received an unexpected order. Ordered a chicken burger and pulled beef sandwich BUT didnt get what we thought it was.

D chicken burger was actually Chicken Ham burger, not a patty.. so it was already a let down from the start. Next our pulled beef sandwich is supposedly from the term, "pulled beef". BUT we received a Big Piece of Salami type of sandwich.

Duno who to blame, d management who chose d ingredients OR d staff who may have actually pulled a fast one. So ya, we didnt really enjoy our food, so be careful wen u do order yours.

Nonetheless, d breads sold at d bakery tasted as how it is supposed to.. yummmmyyyy!!

So ya, have a great munch!!

Cheers!!

#famwithsten #conato #conatobakery #conatobakerycafe #bali #bread #pulledbeefsandwich #chickenburger #feltcheated
review 4: the staffs are so friendly and nice! they even recommend some menu thats match our preference. the place is cozy and great. the foods are yummy!
